Qutuy-tu yeke quriyangyui-tu molon toyin bodisadu eke-dür iyen ači tusa-yi ...

md:note.div:
Qutuy-tu yeke quriyangyui-tu molon toyin bodisadu eke-dür iyen ači tusa-yi qariyuluysan namtar-un sudur orusiba = Beretning om den hellige Molon toyin bodhisattva, der havde opnået stor perfektion, genetablerede gode gerninger for sin mor.
Indeholder også mange fine farvelagte illustrationer bl. a. med de otte varme og otte kolde helveder i underverden.
Håndskrift fra 1800-tallet.
Mong. 417

Qutuy-tu yeke quriyangyui-tu molon toyin bodisadu eke-dür iyen ači tusa-yi qariyuluysan namtar-un sudur orusiba = Tale (how) the saintly Molon toyin Bodhisattva, who attained great perfection, repaid good actions to his mother.
Manuscript (19th century) with many fine colour illuminations depicting the eight hot and cold hells.
Mong. 417
